title: BIG FACTS feat. OJ DA JUICEMAN
itunes:title: BIG FACTS feat. OJ DA JUICEMAN
description:
The BIG FACTS posse discuss the term G.O.A.T. to start off this episode.

Trap Rap legend OJ DA JUICEMAN discusses his battles with diabetes, coming up with Gucci Mane, past business issues with Debra Antney, legal trapping, mixtapes and more with the BIG FACTS crew.
